{"product_id":"solid-linden-flower-shampoo-with-nordic-birch-extract","title":"Magrada Volumizing Solid Shampoo With Linden Flower Extract 58g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGentle on your hair, and on the environment. The solid shampoo concentrate will last longer, while the packaging is made of recycled aluminium.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe richly foaming shampoo protects and conditions, softening and moisturising the scalp as well as the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe organic Nordic birch extract stimulates the circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, thereby accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo is ideal for women, men, as well as children for daily use, and is also suitable for sensitive and delicate scalps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe Nordic birch extract\u003c\/span\u003e, cocoa butter and dried herb inflorescences create a powerful trio which not only cleans, but also makes the hair livelier and fuller, not to mention the honey-sweet scent adding sugary notes to your day.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDried linden flowers\u003c\/span\u003e have an antioxidative and anti-inflammatory effect on The skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids which help to improve The protective function of The skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to The hair and improves The structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract*, Polyquaternium-7, Aqua, Panthenol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Alcohol, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower, Glycerin, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-GB\"\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 96,5%.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Default\"\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927702810951,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-volumizing-solid-shampoo-with-linden-flower-extract-58g-5420286.png?v=1763665704","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/solid-linden-flower-shampoo-with-nordic-birch-extract","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}